      ******************************************************************
       Procedure Division                using d-gfl-exe              .
      ******************************************************************

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Main program                                              *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       main-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione status di uscita                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   d-gfl-exe-exi-sts      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione in funzione del tipo operazione      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Open                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        d-gfl-exe-tip-ope    =    "OP"
                     perform opn-000      thru opn-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Close                                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   d-gfl-exe-tip-ope    =    "CL"
                     perform cls-000      thru cls-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test cancellabilita' modulo                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   d-gfl-exe-tip-ope    =    "C?"
                     perform tcm-000      thru tcm-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Generazione file                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   d-gfl-exe-tip-ope    =    "GF"
                     perform gfl-000      thru gfl-999                .
       main-999.
           exit program.

      *    *===========================================================*
